snippet.title: MLS, Week 25: Seattle Beats Chivas, SJ Clinches Playoff Spot
snippet.description:
MLS, Week 25: Seattle Beats Chivas, SJ Clinches Playoff Spot by Ryan Rosenblatt on Sep 5 2012, 7:22p
Eddie Johnson scored in the 89th minute to win it for Seattle, while the Chivas loss made San Jose the first team in MLS to clinch a playoff spot.

snippet.description:
MLS, Week 25 Preview And Matches: And They Said They Wouldn't Play On International Dates by Ryan Rosenblatt on Sep 4 2012, 8:01a
MLS is taking international dates off, but that doesn't mean you'll get to see all of your favorite players.
